[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    167[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **The problem:** "The dominant architecture for the past few years has been transformer-based models (BERT and its variants), fine-tuned on domain-specific data." This is one of the longer sentences in the recipe. It's still clear, but the parenthetical plus the comma-clause plus the participial phrase makes it denser than the surrounding sentences.
