[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Both `amazon-comprehend-examples` and `amazon-comprehend-medical-fhir-integration` are known aws-samples repositories. The `amazon-comprehend-custom-entity` repo is also valid. All three are appropriately framed as "demonstrate patterns used here."
