[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The subsection covering mixed sentiment as norm, clinical/emotional language intersection, indirectness patterns, cultural variation, and PHI contamination is genuinely educational. This is the kind of content that makes the cookbook valuable beyond a typical AWS tutorial. A reader building a healthcare sentiment system will avoid real pitfalls because of this section.
