[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The related recipes section connects to Recipe 8.1 (same chapter foundation), Recipe 2.1 (LLM alternative), Recipe 4.2 (downstream use of sentiment), and Recipe 10.2 (voice-to-text feeding this pipeline). These create useful navigation paths for readers with different starting points.
