[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m "The demo looks amazing and production looks humbling" is exactly right. The advice about aggregate trends surviving individual errors, and the guidance about who should see raw comments versus aggregated themes, demonstrates real operational experience. This section alone justifies the cookbook's existence over generic documentation.
